00:10:50.126 --> 00:10:51.414
dos bruderl?

00:10:50.593 --> 00:10:59.159
azoy, dem bruderl hot men genumen azoy vi me hot mir ts-, mir hot men tsugekhapt in dray un ferts- in dray un fertsik iz dos geven shoyn.

00:10:59.335 --> 00:11:06.619
un mayn muter iz gekumen oykhet. hot dos gemuzt zayn in di tsayt azoy, hot men di kinder avekgefirt nokh AUSCHWITZ, ye.

00:11:06.777 --> 00:11:13.965
iz, iz zi geblibn, mayn muter, aleyn, ober ikh hob ir nit gezen biz shpeter, shpeter, ven ikh hob

00:11:13.965 --> 00:11:15.647
marshirt un ir getrofn.

00:11:15.771 --> 00:11:21.505
un nakher zaynen mir geven, hot men, nakher hot men undz shoyn gegebn arbetn.

00:11:21.505 --> 00:11:30.712
far di gantse dray teg vos m'hot undz nit gegebn, hot, hot men shoyn gearbet in di velder un in di felder un me hot gehorevet, UNK...

00:11:29.608 --> 00:11:31.638
vifl meydlekh zayt ir geven

00:11:31.638 --> 00:11:32.775
tsuzamen?

00:11:32.410 --> 00:11:37.264
o⟨h,⟩ dortn? geven a por hundert, efsher, in dem lager. hot men oyfgekha- a por hundert.

00:11:36.983 --> 00:11:41.601
un ven m'hot aykh gegebn arbet, hot men genumen di gantse grupe in eynem?

00:11:40.442 --> 00:11:43.713
me hot genum- NO, ⟨ge- ey-⟩ s'iz geven in grupes,

00:11:43.713 --> 00:11:54.594
un eyner iz gegangen in dem zayt vald, eyner gegangen, in an ander, v-, ye. m'hot genumen grupes un m'hot undz, ye. un mir hobn gezegn beymer un m'hot gehakt di beymer. dos iz geven in Estland.

00:11:54.600 --> 00:12:01.023
un oykhet bay di banen, un farshiden- un nakher iz geven ander, hot men geCLEANt bay di daytshn.

00:12:01.333 --> 00:12:02.925
s'iz,

00:12:02.925 --> 00:12:05.242
farshidene arbetn, ⟨obe-⟩...

00:12:03.898 --> 00:12:05.816
vos hot ir genoy geton?

00:12:05.670 --> 00:12:08.549
ikh hob, dortn hob ikh gehakt beymer.

00:12:09.045 --> 00:12:11.699
kh'hob gehakt, m'hot gezegn beymer.

00:12:11.699 --> 00:12:15.032
m'hot i- untergezegt beymer un m'hot gemuzt tsehakn

00:12:15.032 --> 00:12:20.497
un shlepn zey oyfleygn., dos, hob ikh in di velder, ye, dortn gearbet, ye.

00:12:20.706 --> 00:12:22.019
un nakher,

00:12:22.019 --> 00:12:24.213
hot men aroysgenumen vayter,

00:12:24.213 --> 00:12:30.456
un m'hot nokh mentsh- un s'iz gevorn nokh lagern shpeter, un nokh lagern. m'hot gebrakht nokh mentshn fun Vilne.

00:12:30.456 --> 00:12:38.638
un di, fun, di baleb- d- iber undz zaynen geven, fun Holand soldatn. zey hobn undz,

00:12:38.712 --> 00:12:41.153
gehit in di velder bay der arbet.

00:12:41.293 --> 00:12:42.572
fun Holand?

00:12:41.783 --> 00:12:42.809
Holand.

00:12:42.809 --> 00:12:44.510
zey zaynen Holender.

00:12:43.487 --> 00:12:46.053
Natsis? ⟨f- ⟩...?

00:12:45.073 --> 00:12:51.007
 s'iz nit ale geven Natsis. s'iz geven ⟨natsye,⟩ vos zey ⟨zaynen,⟩ mitn daytsh gearbet.

00:12:51.283 --> 00:12:55.541
i- zey zayn- hobn gearbet, ober s'iz geven eynike gants fayne fun zey.

00:12:55.541 --> 00:12:57.136
ye. fun di holender.

00:12:57.136 --> 00:13:03.157
un eynike zaynen oykh geven, vos m'hot zey, zaynen oykh geven oyf arbet, nor zey zaynen geven iber undz, ye.

00:13:03.501 --> 00:13:14.025
un, nakher iz fun dem lager hot men undz genumen in an ander..., dos iz geven Vayvare. der lager hot geheysn Vayvare. der ershter lager iz geven Vayvare in Estland.

00:13:08.550 --> 00:13:13.096
⟨⟩, Vayvare heyst dos? un dos iz in Estland?

00:13:14.149 --> 00:13:18.061
nakher hot men undz genumen avek a bisl tsayt. hot men oysgeklibn epes,

00:13:18.061 --> 00:13:23.289
 tsvantsik froyen un akhtsik mener, epes bay a hundert man, un m'hot undz avekgefirt

00:13:23.599 --> 00:13:27.913
in AUVERE, oykhet in Estland, an ander lager.

00:13:27.970 --> 00:13:28.656
ye.

00:13:28.678 --> 00:13:32.928
un dortn iz oykhet alts geven shvartse arbet, alts iz...

00:13:32.928 --> 00:13:37.883
nor ikh, tsufelik bin ikh punkt dortn arayn arbetn in a kikh,

00:13:37.883 --> 00:13:38.547
in kikh,

00:13:38.547 --> 00:13:44.856
tsu, oyfts- tsukokhn dem kesl in der fri, heyse vaser tsu gebn ts- vos m'iz gegangen tsu der arbet.

00:13:44.980 --> 00:13:51.943
un me fleg darfn, fun, arayntrogn a gantsn kesl vaser fun brunem, araynshlepn emers vaser

00:13:52.084 --> 00:13:54.047
tsu makhn ful dem kesl,

00:13:54.047 --> 00:14:00.600
un tsugreytn, sheyln kartofl, un tsugreytn, helfn dortn di kekhin mit, mit di andere in kikh.

00:14:01.011 --> 00:14:03.317
un, dortn...

00:14:02.614 --> 00:14:04.515
vos hobn di andere geton?

00:14:04.420 --> 00:14:06.923
di andere zaynen aroys tsu der arbet,

00:14:06.782 --> 00:14:08.092
vos far a arbet?

00:14:06.923 --> 00:14:08.045
in droysn.

00:14:08.045 --> 00:14:11.023
oykhet oyf banen, in velder,

00:14:11.023 --> 00:14:14.167
⟨i- ts-,⟩ bay daytshn geCLEANt,

00:14:14.933 --> 00:14:17.121
farshidene arbetn azoyne.

00:14:15.945 --> 00:14:19.364
mit, mit holts oykh?, holts,

00:14:19.573 --> 00:14:21.599
beymer arbet?

00:14:20.502 --> 00:14:23.393
oykhet, ye. farshidene arbetn oykh.

00:14:22.003 --> 00:14:23.316
un griber g-

00:14:23.316 --> 00:14:24.815
grobn griber?

00:14:23.393 --> 00:14:26.480
 griber, ye, farshidene azoyne, ye.

00:14:26.480 --> 00:14:28.935
un, in dem lager,

00:14:28.935 --> 00:14:35.871
hob ikh aykh dertseylt, vos ikh hob getrofn m⟨a-⟩ dem TEACHER, mayner a, fun der heym iz er geven a TEACHER,

00:14:35.871 --> 00:14:39.075
un bay undz oyfn hoyf hot di mame zayne gevoynt.

00:14:39.098 --> 00:14:41.488
un er hot gehat a yingl in mayn elter.

00:14:42.220 --> 00:14:43.884
un er,

00:14:44.160 --> 00:14:50.164
zet oys az fun hunger, dar, oysgedart, hot, iz di hoyzn im aropgefaln mistomen.

00:14:50.164 --> 00:14:55.882
er ⟨iz⟩ gegangen arbetn, hot er gearbet epes bay poyerim, zet oys, dortn, oyf a feld.

00:14:56.192 --> 00:14:58.416
tsi er hot genumen a pasik,

00:14:58.416 --> 00:15:01.265
tsi a shtrik tsu farbindn di hoyzn,

00:15:02.183 --> 00:15:04.659
veys ikh, az er hot,

00:15:04.659 --> 00:15:07.053
az m'iz gekumen fun der arbet...

00:15:07.903 --> 00:15:11.727
dos iz geven in ovnt, ven m'iz gekumen fun der arbet in lager arayn...

00:15:11.785 --> 00:15:14.091
iz geshtanen der S.S.-man,

00:15:14.468 --> 00:15:15.677
der daytsh,

00:15:15.902 --> 00:15:17.938
un er hot im aroysgenumen,

00:15:18.602 --> 00:15:23.996
un er hot im tseshtokhn mit a shpiz, mit a, mit a bagnet.

00:15:21.690 --> 00:15:22.426
mit,

00:15:23.850 --> 00:15:25.784
mit vos hot er im bashuldikt?

00:15:26.027 --> 00:15:32.754
az ⟨e- e-⟩ s'hot mistom⟨e⟩ dortn, vu er hot gearbet, hot gezogt az er hot genumen a sht- pasik tsu di hoyzn.

00:15:31.782 --> 00:15:32.926
geganvet?

00:15:32.760 --> 00:15:34.979
⟨geg-, g-⟩...

00:15:32.926 --> 00:15:35.943
hot er ge- bashuldikt az er hot geganvet?

00:15:34.979 --> 00:15:45.697
gega- efsher hot er genumen a shtrik oder a pasik; di hoyzn z⟨aynen⟩ aropgefaln, hot er efsh- efsher. ikh veys nit. kh'ken aykh nit zogn genoy, vayl ikh hob dokh nit ⟨gekent⟩ fregn im oder ikh ho- m'hot dokh moyre gehat.

00:15:45.788 --> 00:15:51.519
nor eyns: az vi s'iz ongekumen di partye, iz der S.S. im aroysgenumen,

00:15:51.762 --> 00:15:53.970
un aroysgenumen di bagnet.

00:15:53.970 --> 00:15:56.598
es geyt ⟨aza kh-⟩, azoy vi a meser, a bagnet.

00:15:56.757 --> 00:15:57.864
un er hot im

00:15:58.090 --> 00:15:59.400
geshtokhn

00:15:59.473 --> 00:16:01.816
etlekhe mol in kerper,

00:16:01.816 --> 00:16:07.250
un er hot im gevorfn, gedreyt, azoy vi, azoy vi a, es dreyt zikh a balo- a

00:16:07.250 --> 00:16:08.191
balon.

00:16:08.974 --> 00:16:11.713
un er, der man hot geshrien,

00:16:11.713 --> 00:16:13.136
hot ir gehert

00:16:13.311 --> 00:16:18.362
far kilometers. un me hot im nakher, az er iz shoyn geven tseshtokhn,

00:16:18.362 --> 00:16:20.662
un m'hot im arayngedreyt azoy,

00:16:21.006 --> 00:16:24.831
dortn iz geven a, a k- a kemerl,

00:16:24.938 --> 00:16:31.682
vu s'iz gelegn di toyte. s'flegt ale mol shtarbn a mentsh:, hunger, kelt, TYPHUS, mit alts.

00:16:31.806 --> 00:16:34.837
un m'hot im dortn aroyfgevorfn. s'iz shoyn geven

00:16:34.843 --> 00:16:37.400
kalt azoy, harbst mistomen,

00:16:37.577 --> 00:16:46.042
un der man iz oyf di toyte gelegn a gantse nakht, un er hot geshrien; nit geveynt, nor geshrien far veytik,

00:16:46.268 --> 00:16:48.821
az s'hot geklungen azoy, UNK, a- a-

00:16:48.821 --> 00:16:55.137
a- az di mentshn... m'hot dos nit gekent bagrayfn, di ge-, di gevaldn, azoy vi me shekht vemen.

00:16:55.178 --> 00:16:57.343
biz er iz geshtorbn in der fri,

00:16:57.343 --> 00:17:01.601
⟨hot er,⟩ der man, ikh hob im gekent, a sh- fayner TEACHER iz geven.

00:17:01.472 --> 00:17:02.866
vi hot er geheysn?

00:17:03.143 --> 00:17:03.862
I,

00:17:04.358 --> 00:17:15.995
ikh veys, di mame hot geheysn Nekhame di l-, di kremerke, vayle zi hot gehat a krom bay undz, un er fleg kumen. ober ikh zol gedenken zayn nomen, veys i-... un Khaim iz geven der, a bruder vos hot gevoynt mit di mamen.

00:17:16.069 --> 00:17:21.817
un er fl- er hot dokh shoyn nit gevoynt bay undz, nor er fleg kumen, hob ikh nor im, ober ikh ken nit.

00:17:20.963 --> 00:17:23.994
iz geve- er geven a sakh elter fun aykh, mistome?

00:17:23.511 --> 00:17:28.804
er iz geven shoyn a TEACHER, un er hot gehat a zun vi ikh. iz er dokh shoyn geven a, ye.

00:17:28.860 --> 00:17:32.718
ober ikh hob im, fleg im zen; er fleg kumen tsu di mamen ⟨i-,⟩ ye.

00:17:32.893 --> 00:17:36.671
un in lager iz er geven ⟨un⟩ hob ikh gezen di mayse, ye.

00:17:36.671 --> 00:17:42.720
⟨oh⟩, azoy, biz haynt her ikh di gevaldn zayne. a mol ikh, zits azoy un ikh dermon zikh fun im, iz, ⟨⟩,

00:17:42.720 --> 00:17:47.889
geyt mir durkh a shoyder az ikh dermon zikh; ikh hob im azoy gekent, aza fayner man geven.

00:17:47.862 --> 00:17:49.540
ho- hobn di,

00:17:49.540 --> 00:17:55.077
 di andere meydlekh gezogt epes e- eyner tsu dem tsveytn tsum treystn?

00:17:52.292 --> 00:17:54.722
UNK... ⟨tor⟩⟨UNK⟩...

00:17:55.152 --> 00:18:02.993
tsum treystn, ken men zikh treystn, ober mer hot men ⟨zi⟩kh nit gekent. vos hot men gekent? m'hot dokh moyre gehat. haynt iz er, morgn ken zayn ikh.

00:18:03.015 --> 00:18:06.552
iber morgn, tomer lakh ikh efsher, tomer gey ikh nit glaykh,

00:18:06.863 --> 00:18:09.745
tomer hob ikh gegebn a hust, ober a nis,

00:18:09.745 --> 00:18:14.265
ken ikh zayn di zelbe kapore-hindl bay zey. bay zey hot geshpilt a role, vos?

00:18:15.334 --> 00:18:20.559
bay zey hot ir nit ge-... tomer hot ir gegebn a drey di kop efsher nit, ⟨az⟩ ir zayt geshtanen oyf an apel,

00:18:20.768 --> 00:18:24.913
un ir zayt nit geshtanen glaykh, hot ⟨e⟩r shoyn, UNK ⟨m'hot dokh⟩ ⟨UNK⟩geshtanen.

00:18:25.122 --> 00:18:28.255
nu, dervayl-, un dos iz geven

00:18:28.260 --> 00:18:31.679
in, dervayle bin ikh krank gevorn oyf TYPHUS,

00:18:32.496 --> 00:18:34.059
bin ikh krank gevorn.

00:18:34.521 --> 00:18:45.180
un ikh bin gelegn oyf dr'erd. s'iz geven aza ⟨oy-⟩ es hot geheysn a "shpitol." fun a blekhene pushke aza, gemakht aza TSERIF,

00:18:45.372 --> 00:18:48.572
a, aza hoyz... vi zol UNK dos zogn?

00:18:48.645 --> 00:18:51.052
un m'iz gelegn oyf dr'erd oyf shtroy.

00:18:51.598 --> 00:18:58.207
un s'iz geven vinter; di vaser iz geven farfrorn, vayl s'iz kalt geven dortn. s'iz dokh lem vasern, s'iz dokh...

00:18:58.838 --> 00:19:06.341
un di hits iz geven groys, un keyn meditsin mit dos iz nit geven. iz men gelegn; ver s'iz geshtorbn iz geshtorbn.

00:19:06.364 --> 00:19:09.125
ir zayt ⟨aven⟩, ale- geven aleyn,

00:19:10.259 --> 00:19:12.433
in dem krankn, shtibele?

00:19:11.005 --> 00:19:16.360
NO, NO, NO! s'iz geven dortn nokh. ver s'iz gevorn krank, s'iz ge- arumgegange-...

00:19:14.717 --> 00:19:16.685
vifl, vifl froyen,

00:19:16.405 --> 00:19:20.972
e- es iz geven efsher a fuftsn mentshn, ye. s'iz geven, s'-...

00:19:16.911 --> 00:19:18.086
umgefer?

00:19:20.100 --> 00:19:22.625
mener mit froyen, tsi nor froyen?

00:19:22.682 --> 00:19:24.511
mener mit froyen, ye.

00:19:24.511 --> 00:19:31.434
s'iz geven eyn barak, eyn, ye. f- un s'iz geven fun blekh aza r⟨u-⟩ a halb-rundiker azoy. iz nokh kelter vi fun holts.

00:19:31.609 --> 00:19:39.495
 nor di hits iz geven azoy groys az s'iz shoyn kalt nit geven. un ⟨d- na-⟩ un m'hot nit gekent esn, un az m'hot shoyn gekent esn iz nit geven vos tsu esn.

00:19:39.495 --> 00:19:41.469
m'hot nakher arayngegebn epes.

00:19:41.469 --> 00:19:46.427
un s'iz arumgegangen der TYPHUS, un ikh hob gehat a boykh-tifus un a lungen-ontsind-

00:19:46.427 --> 00:19:48.343
m'iz dokh gelegn azoy in hits,

00:19:48.585 --> 00:19:50.283
un nakher

00:19:50.762 --> 00:19:54.924
hot men zikh dervu- ⟨he- he-⟩ m'hot zikh nit dervust, nor me hot gehert

00:19:55.268 --> 00:19:56.342
az

00:19:56.415 --> 00:19:57.669
di rusn,

00:19:57.669 --> 00:20:00.864
di milkhome, di rusn dernentern zikh tsu Nar⟨ve⟩.

00:20:02.254 --> 00:20:03.041
nu...

00:20:02.254 --> 00:20:05.572
⟨f- v-⟩ vos iz di tsayt itst? dos iz in

00:20:05.663 --> 00:20:08.829
vinter in dray un fertsik, fir un fertsik?

00:20:06.338 --> 00:20:08.734
dos iz geven,

00:20:08.734 --> 00:20:20.962
⟨, 'BOUT⟩ azoy, ye, in dray un fertsik, ye, bayn ende azoy, ye, ye. bayn ende umgefer. m'hot nit gevust keyn dates; m'hot nit gehat keyn CALENDAR, m'hot nit gevust ve- vosere tog un vosere yor.

00:20:12.160 --> 00:20:13.470
bay⟨n⟩ detsember?

00:20:21.019 --> 00:20:23.696
m'hot nor m- mer-veyniker gevust azoy.

00:20:23.922 --> 00:20:25.378
iz,

00:20:25.378 --> 00:20:26.373
hot men

00:20:26.373 --> 00:20:31.577
genumen dem gantse kranke un m'hot aroyf- avekgefirt nokh AUSCHWITZ.

00:20:31.768 --> 00:20:33.091
un mir mit

00:20:33.091 --> 00:20:41.364
nokh a meydl hot men oysgeshribn. far vos? kh'hob gearbet in kikh, iz, vi me zogt, dos iz efsher protektsye, efsher mazl. ikh veys nit vos tsu zogn.

00:20:41.995 --> 00:20:49.954
un ⟨az ikh bin⟩ shoyn arayn in lager, yene hot men avekgefirt. vu, hot men dokh oykh nit gevust. nakher hot zikh aroysgevizn az m'hot zey avekgefirt nokh AUSCHWITZ.

00:20:50.061 --> 00:20:51.185
⟨kh'⟩bin arayn...

00:20:50.112 --> 00:20:52.890
ve- ver iz dos geven vos hot aykh geratevet?

00:20:53.959 --> 00:21:06.148
fun lager, hot men mir oysgeshribn, der, vos ikh ho-, der lager-firer, a yidisher, Yankelevitsh. er iz geven a yidisher. er iz oykh gelegn oyfn TYPHUS, nakher iz er aroys. ober er iz geven der lager-fir-...

00:21:05.080 --> 00:21:06.258
⟨ho- iz⟩ a man?

00:21:06.148 --> 00:21:10.254
er iz a man geven, Yankelevitsh. er iz, in Vilne hobn zey gehat a shnit-gevelb,

00:21:06.258 --> 00:21:07.065
⟨ah⟩...

00:21:10.665 --> 00:21:11.995
 a groysn.

00:21:11.995 --> 00:21:17.007
un a fayner man geven, un er hot gehat a tokhter in an ander lager. efsher hot er gefilt

00:21:17.007 --> 00:21:23.028
tsu mir vi a kin- ikh f- ken aykh nit... efsher hot er gefilt, vayl er hot, ⟨hot⟩ gehat a tokhter in mayn elter,

00:21:23.136 --> 00:21:24.801
un er hot...

00:21:24.925 --> 00:21:26.470
hot er mir oysgeshribn,

00:21:26.470 --> 00:21:27.686
un ikh hob g-, ye.

00:21:27.793 --> 00:21:29.120
un THEN,

00:21:29.579 --> 00:21:32.692
 iz, hob ikh gemeynt, in lager

00:21:32.692 --> 00:21:40.308
vel ikh epes ersht esn, efsher vo-... gekent hob ikh nit shteln a fus fun danet biz danet; ikh bin geven azoy oysgeshvakht,

00:21:40.308 --> 00:21:42.274
krank, oysgekrenkt,

00:21:42.274 --> 00:21:43.143
hungerik.

00:21:43.285 --> 00:21:45.889
hob ikh gemeynt, in lager, kh'vel zayn efsher,

00:21:45.889 --> 00:21:47.923
vel ikh a bisl kumen tsu zikh.

00:21:47.923 --> 00:21:50.636
a bisl zup, efsher dos; kh'hob gehat a khaverte,

00:21:50.710 --> 00:21:53.387
 hot zi mir gegebn epes.

00:21:53.848 --> 00:21:55.794
in tsvey teg,

00:21:55.794 --> 00:21:59.775
hot genumen az mir darfn ale marshirn, vayle

00:22:00.362 --> 00:22:02.557
me firt undz alemen aroyset.

00:22:02.775 --> 00:22:09.080
oder vos un ven, hot men dokh UNK nit gezogt, far vos me firt undz. nakher hot men zikh dervust, di rusn hobn genumen

00:22:09.171 --> 00:22:12.062
geyn farne- hobn zey farnumen Narve.

00:22:12.062 --> 00:22:14.801
hot men dokh undz nit lozn epes bafrayen,

00:22:14.875 --> 00:22:18.919
hot men genumen marshirn un geyn in an ander lager.

00:22:19.060 --> 00:22:21.399
